OL,3,CThree teens took turns raping 13-year-
OL,4,Cold girl in the bushes, jury told
OL,6,FThree boys "took it in turns" to rape
OL,7,Fa 13-year-old girl in Rochdale and
OL,8,Ffilmed part of the attack on a mobile
OL,9,Fphone, a jury has been told.
OL,11,FProsecutors told a jury at
OL,12,FManchester's Minshull Street Crown
OL,13,FCourt that the boys, who were aged 12,
OL,14,F13 and 14 at the time later circulated
OL,15,Fthe footage among themselves and
OL,16,Fothers.
OL,18,FThe three boys, who cannot be named
OL,19,Ffor legal reasons, deny the charges
OL,20,Fthey face.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
