PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772637083
OL,3,CThree teens took turns raping 13-year-
OL,4,Cold girl in the bushes, jury told
OL,6,FThe teenage girl, who also cannot be
OL,7,Fnamed for legal reasons, was allegedly
OL,8,Fraped just off a footpath near to
OL,9,FNewbold tram stop in Rochdale in
OL,10,FFebruary 2024.
OL,12,FTwo of the boys, now aged 15 and 16,
OL,13,Fare standing trial at Manchester's
OL,14,FMinshull Street Crown Court. The third
OL,15,Fwho was aged 12 at the time, has been
OL,16,Fdeemed unfit to stand trial, the jury
OL,17,Fwas told as the case opened on 3 March.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772637083
OL,3,CThree teens took turns raping 13-year-
OL,4,Cold girl in the bushes, jury told
OL,6,FKim Whittlestone, prosecuting, said:
OL,7,F"The prosecution say that these
OL,8,Fdefendants acted together. She was a
OL,9,F13-year-old girl at the time, didn't
OL,10,Fknow them, they weren't friends and
OL,11,Fthey had been in her company for a
OL,12,Fvery short period of time."
OL,14,FThe jury was told the girl was
OL,15,F"physically pushed and bent over
OL,16,Fforward" as she was raped. Ms
OL,17,FWhittlestone said the boys then "all
OL,18,Fswapped."
OL,20,FShe said it "would have been obvious"
OL,21,Fthat she "did not want this to happen."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772637083
OL,3,CThree teens took turns raping 13-year-
OL,4,Cold girl in the bushes, jury told
OL,6,FMs Whittlestone said it was the
OL,7,Fprosecution's case that the now 15 and
OL,8,F16-year-olds "are guilty of rape" and
OL,9,Fthat "they knew what consent meant."
OL,11,FShe said: "You will hear in this case
OL,12,Fthat as part of their defence they
OL,13,Fwill say that she consented to some
OL,14,Fsexual activity and she instigated it.
OL,16,F"So, there can be no doubt that they
OL,17,Fknew what consent meant."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772637083
OL,3,CThree teens took turns raping 13-year-
OL,4,Cold girl in the bushes, jury told
OL,6,FThe trial was told a friend the girl
OL,7,Fwas with "stepped in to stop what was
OL,8,Fhappening" and the defendants ran away
OL,9,Ffrom the scene.
OL,11,FJurors were told "some" of what
OL,12,Fallegedly happened was filmed on a
OL,13,Fmobile phone. The girl, said the
OL,14,Fprosecutor, was "not asked if she
OL,15,Fconsented to filming."
OL,17,F"You will watch that footage, a short
OL,18,F10 second clip, but it will give you
OL,19,Fan insight into the attitude of the
OL,20,Fdefendants," Ms Whittlestone told the
OL,21,Fjury.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
