PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772637083
OL,3,CThree teens took turns raping 13-year-
OL,4,Cold girl in the bushes, jury told
OL,6,FShe went on to say: "Later that night
OL,7,Fthey circulated amongst themselves and
OL,8,Fto others that footage."JMs
OL,9,FWhittlestone said the third boy, who
OL,10,Fis now 14, was "an active participant
OL,11,Fin what occurred."
OL,13,FThe friend the girl was with told
OL,14,Fpolice she heard one of the boys
OL,15,Fsaying "let me have a go now," she
OL,16,Fadded.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
