OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772637083
OL,3,CThree teens took turns raping 13-year-
OL,4,Cold girl in the bushes, jury told
OL,6,FIt is alleged the girl was taken into
OL,7,Fthe bushes by the now 15 year-old, who
OL,8,Fwas joined by the other two. "The
OL,9,Fprosecution say that they took it in
OL,10,Fturns and swapped positions," Ms
OL,11,FWhittlestone said.
OL,13,FShe was asked if she wanted to have
OL,14,Fsex and replied "no," the jury heard.
OL,15,FThat was heard by the friend she was
OL,16,Fwith, the court was told.
OL,18,FMs Whittlestone said the defendants
OL,19,F"overpowered" the girl. The teenage
OL,20,Fgirl said in police interviews that
OL,21,Fshe was scared, the prosecutor said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772637083
OL,3,CThree teens took turns raping 13-year-
OL,4,Cold girl in the bushes, jury told
OL,6,F"She told them she felt panicked and
OL,7,Fdidn't know what to do," the
OL,8,Fprosecutor added. "She said that 'her
OL,9,Fhead was going 100 miles per hour' and
OL,10,F'it was horrible'."
OL,12,FThe jury was told the boys were seen
OL,13,Fon CCTV in Rochdale town centre
OL,14,Ftalking to some girls before heading
OL,15,Fto Rochdale tram station. The alleged
OL,16,Fvictim, who later told police she was
OL,17,Fgoing to McDonald's, was waiting at
OL,18,Fthe stop with a friend, the court
OL,19,Fheard.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772637083
OL,3,CThree teens took turns raping 13-year-
OL,4,Cold girl in the bushes, jury told
OL,6,FThey all got on a tram and got off at
OL,7,FNewbold, it was said.
OL,9,F"There is some interaction on the
OL,10,Ftram, but not consistently throughout
OL,11,Fthe journey," Ms Whittlestone said,
OL,12,Ftelling the jury the boys were
OL,13,F"blocking" the path of the girls when
OL,14,Fthey all got off at Newbold.
OL,16,FThe jury heard they were "manhandled
OL,17,Fby the boys."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
