OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772637083
OL,3,CThree teens took turns raping 13-year-
OL,4,Cold girl in the bushes, jury told
OL,6,FMs Whittlestone said: "Shortly after
OL,7,Fleaving the station the offence occurs
OL,8,Fin bushes off a pathway leading from
OL,9,Fthe tram stop.
OL,11,F"She said it all happened in a blur in
OL,12,Fa short space of time. The prosecution
OL,13,Fsay that their actions were part of a
OL,14,Fjoint enterprise to rape her."
OL,16,FThe indictment contains five counts of
OL,17,Frape. Three counts relate specifically
OL,18,Fto each boy, while two are charged as
OL,19,F"joint enterprise," jurors were told.
OL,20,FEach boy denies the charges they face.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
